data.description: Unveil the epitome of comfort and luxury in this stunning 6 bedroom, 4 bathroom abode nestled on Monument's southside. Revel in the seamless blend of elegance and functionality with an open floor plan, rich hardwood floors, and captivating bay windows. Indulge in culinary delights in the gourmet kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, Quartz countertops, and a pop of color on the island. Step outside to a sprawling porch overlooking the fully landscaped yard, perfect for alfresco dining or unwinding in a hot tub. With a master suite, finished basement, and proximity to schools, trails, and amenities, this home promises an unparalleled lifestyle. Don't hesitate—schedule your showing today and seize this exceptional opportunity!
